Export the design to xlsx

Source: R/export.R
export_design.Rd

This function is designed to export the design made using edibble to an external xlsx file.

export_design(.data, file, author, date = Sys.Date(), overwrite = FALSE)

Arguments

.data

An edibble data frame or design.
file

File, including the path, to export the data to.
author

Name of the author in character. A vector of character is supported for where there are multiple authors.
date

The date to be inserted in header.
overwrite

A logical indicating whether to overwrite exisitng file or not.

See also

Other user-facing functions: allocate_trts(), design-context, expect_vars(), randomise_trts(), record_vars(), serve_table(), set_trts(), set_units(), start_design()
